    "display_name": "Choose a Song",
    "long_instructions": "### Choose a Song\r\n\r\nNow it's your turn to take everything you've learned and make it your own! Choose a song to create a remix for!\r\n\r\nIf you want to pick a new song, you can click the restart button in the upper-right corner [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=start-over-button)\r\n\r\n**Do This**:\r\n- Start to build your snippets - use functions to combine together interesting tracks and effects in unique ways\r\n- Combine into a bigger song - combine your functions together to create your larger remix\r\n- Experiment! Rearrange the functions, try out new tracks - reinvent the song in your own way!\r\n\r\n",
